  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1020550/extras/870c71ab754572fdba7fb728428db384.poster.avif?t=1762559465\" width=546 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1020550/extras/870c71ab754572fdba7fb728428db384.webm?t=1762559465\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1020550/extras/870c71ab754572fdba7fb728428db384.mp4?t=1762559465\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>CHROMA+ELEKTRON is a fast-paced 2D shooter with an emphasis on high-speed movement.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Increasingly difficult waves of enemies. </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Collect their energy and unleash powerful weapons and abilities. </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Return all chromatic energy to its proper state. </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Your speed and power will know no equal.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fast-paced, highly challenging shoot 'em up gameplay: overcome impossible odds.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock 12 weapons and 12 \"burst powers\" to turn the tide.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Over 15 different enemy types including 4 challenging bosses.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >14 unique levels, each with their own layouts, visuals and strategies.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Original soundtrack that builds as you progress through waves of enemies.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Robust scoring system--aim for proficiency and max performance.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Many accessibility options are available, such as difficulty modifiers and control options. Everyone can overcome impossible odds.</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1020550/extras/870c71ab754572fdba7fb728428db384.poster.avif?t=1762559465\" width=546 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1020550/extras/870c71ab754572fdba7fb728428db384.webm?t=1762559465\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1020550/extras/870c71ab754572fdba7fb728428db384.mp4?t=1762559465\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>CHROMA+ELEKTRON is a fast-paced 2D shooter with an emphasis on high-speed movement.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Increasingly difficult waves of enemies. </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Collect their energy and unleash powerful weapons and abilities. </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Return all chromatic energy to its proper state. </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Your speed and power will know no equal.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fast-paced, highly challenging shoot 'em up gameplay: overcome impossible odds.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock 12 weapons and 12 \"burst powers\" to turn the tide.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Over 15 different enemy types including 4 challenging bosses.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >14 unique levels, each with their own layouts, visuals and strategies.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Original soundtrack that builds as you progress through waves of enemies.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Robust scoring system--aim for proficiency and max performance.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Many accessibility options are available, such as difficulty modifiers and control options. Everyone can overcome impossible odds.</p></li></ul>",
